lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">为维护公众利益，深化行业诚信建设，提升上市公司年报审计质量，推动资本市场健康发展，现就各证券资格会计师事务所（以下简称事务所）做好上市公司</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>2017</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年年报审计工作通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.2pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一、总体要求</SPAN></B><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">要以党的十九大精神为指导，做好上市公司</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>2017</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年年报审计工作，始终不忘维护公众利益的初心，时刻牢记服务国家建设的使命，深入贯彻中共中央、国务院《关于开展质量提升行动的指导意见》和高质量发展要求，巩固拓展行业质量提升年主题活动成果，强化风险防控，完善内部机制，在执业过程中落实风险导向理念与方法，保持职业怀疑与职业谨慎，勇于直面问题，敢于坚持原则。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.2pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">二、严格遵守职业道德相关规定与要求</SPAN></B><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要认真查找自身在职业道德方面存在的问题与不足，严格落实职业道德的各项规定与要求，健全切实可行且有针对性的相关政策与程序，将职业道德作为业务培训尤其是年报审计业务培训的核心内容；确保在执业过程中遵循诚信、客观、公正原则，保持应有的独立性和专业胜任能力，履行保密义务，维护职业声誉。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">独立性是注册会计师执业的灵魂，事务所要高度重视独立性问题。针对非鉴证业务比重逐年提高的新情况，事务所要更加严格遵守向被审计单位提供非鉴证服务时的独立性要求，正确理解并严格执行定期轮换制度，保持高度警觉，准确识别影响独立性的各种情形，确保职业判断客观、公正，要通过完善独立性声明、从业人员投资申报和内部监控机制等措施，确保从实质上和形式上真正实现独立性。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要积极规范项目工时管理和成本核算，杜绝索取回扣、压价竞争、或有收费等不当行为，实现良性发展，维护良好形象。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.2pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三、强化质量控制体系建设</SPAN></B><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要系统梳理外部监督检查以及内部监控发现的各种质量控制问题，找准质量控制体系存在的短板和薄弱环节，着力强化内部制度、机制建设，切实增强自身</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>“</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">免疫力</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>”</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，推动质量控制体系真正发挥防风险、提质量、促发展的重要作用。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要始终坚持质量至上执业理念，真正落实质量控制领导责任，强化总分所一体化管理，制定并执行全所统一、有效的质量控制政策与程序，尤其应当加强业务承接与保持、业务委派、项目质量控制和报告签发等关键环节的风险管控。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要高度重视业务承接与保持，严格执行风险评估，强化与前任注册会计师的沟通，了解上市公司变更审计机构的真正原因。要从执业质量的角度而非单纯商业利益的角度考虑业务的承接与保持问题，杜绝出现分所或合伙人擅自承接或保持高风险业务的情况。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要建立全所统一的项目管理和人员委派机制，综合考虑业务复杂程度、合伙人专业胜任能力、合伙人业务量等因素进行项目委派，确保委派足够的具有胜任能力的人员，避免出现部分分所或合伙人业务负荷过重、部分项目审计资源配置不足的情况。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22.7pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">事务所要强化高风险业务的项目质量控制复核，特别关注复杂交易或重大事项相关的职业判断的合理性和审计结论的恰当性；要关注质量控制复核意见的落实情况，确保质量控制复核不走过场。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.2pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" 
align=left><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">四、认真贯彻实施新准则</SPAN></B><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: #333333; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
