style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>2016</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>12</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月，财政部批准发布《中国注册会计师审计准则第</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>1504</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">号</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>――</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">在审计报告中沟通关键审计事项》等</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>12</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">项审计准则（以下简称新审计报告准则）；</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "Cambria",serif; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体'>2017</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
